-- AngloGold Says the Suspension at Its Tau Lekoa Mine Lifted After Accident
-- Ron Derby
-- 2010-07-13T09:04:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/anglogold-says-the-suspension-at-its-tau-lekoa-mine-lifted-after-accident.html

          
          
             AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. said a
government suspension of operations at most of its Tau Lekoa
mine in South Africa has been lifted.  
 “A few” parts of the mine are still closed pending
further inspection, spokeswoman Joanne Jones said by mobile
phone today.  
